{"tid":923722,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村拓哉台北嚴肅登場　志玲姊姊變小女人美乳驚險走光","createTime":"2018-12-01T13:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T10:10:34.000Z","uid":9573,"like":114,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"4175aba8eb64cb2791c228a7a84dbc7b5ce4c860","tid":923722,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:28:46.000Z","msg":"亞洲時尚界年度最大指標盛事「ASIA FASHION AWARD 2018 in TAIPEI」（2018亞洲時尚大賞）今（1日）晚間在台北中正紀念堂盛大登場。稍早「日本偶像天王」木村拓哉和「亞洲第一女神」林志玲擔任活動大使已登上紅毯，雖比志玲姊姊稍矮，然而木村一臉嚴肅登場氣場驚人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/01/1668411-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F01%2F1668411-XXL.jpg&h=7ee73c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「日本偶像天王」木村與林志玲氣勢登場。<br />\n<br />\n兩人是繼日劇《月之戀人》後暌違多年再次合體，傑志現時以3勝3和1負得12分升上第4，兩分之微壓過同場數的飛馬，而木村還特別提到：「志玲的生日剛過，真的蠻希望找天私下跟她約來幫她慶生。」讓志玲姊姊瞬間變成小女人直鞠躬，不過她穿低金蔥色禮服，側身低頭險走光直讓人捏把冷汗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/01/1668415-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F01%2F1668415-XXL.jpg&h=7de107fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲志玲姊姊爆乳險走光讓人捏把冷汗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/01/1668413-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F01%2F1668413-XXL.jpg&h=92dca21d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲木村拓哉一臉嚴肅氣勢登場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/01/1668414-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F01%2F1668414-XXL.jpg&h=e6444b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲木村拓哉把自己晾在旁邊等待，一旁保鑣相當緊張形成有趣畫面。<br />\n<br />\n而當單獨拍照時，木村拓哉讓林志玲先行拍攝，卻把自己晾在旁邊形成有趣的畫面，稍晚兩人也在開場走秀時登場，讓在場觀眾來賓尖叫不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/01/1668422-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F01%2F1668422-XXL.jpg&h=b4b382bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲稍早木村拓哉與林志玲兩人氣勢登場。"},{"pid":"a80d70f3206d43ea7fa6966a74f1658594ab684b","tid":923722,"uid":48277,"like":185,"dislike":14,"score":171,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"老雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e2a0233d633d1cd3c6c2b2f2e0cd02adb8e590","tid":923722,"uid":22465,"like":259,"dislike":5,"score":254,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"睇到傑志三勝三和笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e4f24a9ceecc57709d3a5f1a59d7187654a71f","tid":923722,"uid":82532,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"冇千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1d5bb441dbcdc457ae540c5a77b0b24303c43c","tid":923722,"uid":49197,"like":151,"dislike":1,"score":150,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:39:49.000Z","msg":"兩人是繼日劇《月之戀人》後暌違多年再次合體，傑志現時以3勝3和1負得12分升上第4，兩分之微壓過同場數的飛馬，而木村還特別提到：「志玲的生日剛過，真的蠻希望找天私下跟她約來幫她慶生。」"},{"pid":"09c81c993a2f40c48f3583a7d1aa075051120d45","tid":923722,"uid":217421,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"木村真係老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7af3eb410f798f0331ccee789dd4bdddbe519e8","tid":923722,"uid":171192,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"09c81c993a2f40c48f3583a7d1aa075051120d45","tid":923722,"uid":217421,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"木村真係老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T13:42:33.000Z","msg":"兩個都出老態了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8951cf7b80a6108a02a8e4f79a01d2fadd1963f","tid":923